[[SECTION]]
TITLE: Verification scope and results

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: APP-090
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Application preparation verification scope and results
STATEMENT: >>>
Independent verification of the application data preparation outputs was
performed prior to commencement of application testing (Phase 4 of APP-040).

Verification scope:

  a) Application Requirements Specification (APP-010 to APP-030):
       - Completeness: all elements in scope (APP-010) have a corresponding
         functional requirement (APP-020) or are explicitly excluded.
       - Consistency with source data (geographic survey, signalling principles,
         interface control document).
       - Data constraints (APP-030) cover all platform-imposed limits.

  b) Application Architecture and Design (APP-070, APP-080):
       - Module structure is consistent with requirements (APP-020).
       - All Table A.11 techniques required are planned (APP-060).
       - Preparation workflow (APP-080) is complete and consistent with the
         data dictionary and compilation process.
       - Traceability mechanism described in APP-080 is adequate.

  c) Application data source files (initial review):
       - Syntax check: compilation with zero errors and warnings (APP-080).
       - Spot-check of element register against geographic survey.
       - Spot-check of route definitions against signalling principles.
       - All constraint checks (APP-C-001 through APP-C-009) pass in
         validation report.

Verification methods applied (Table A.11):
  Formal design review:  conducted on <YYYY-MM-DD> by <Verifier Name>.
  Walkthrough:           source file walkthrough session on <YYYY-MM-DD>.
  Checklists:            <checklist document ID> applied; all items addressed.
  Fagan inspection:      <reference / N/A — required for SIL≥1>.

Verifier:
  Name:               <Name>
  Organisation:       <Organisation>
  Independence level: <Independent of preparer per SP-021>

Verification results:

  Item                              | Result       | Findings / reference
  ----------------------------------|--------------|----------------------------
  Requirements completeness         | Satisfactory | <None / ref. to findings>
  Requirements–source consistency   | Satisfactory | <None / ref. to findings>
  Architecture module structure     | Satisfactory | <None / ref. to findings>
