  Compilation: zero errors          | PASS         | Log reference: <filename.log>
  Constraint validation: all PASS   | PASS         | Report: <filename.vld>
  Table A.11 techniques planned     | Satisfactory | <see APP-060>

Findings: <None / list with reference to action items>
Verification verdict: <Approved / Approved with conditions / Not approved>
Date of approval: <YYYY-MM-DD>
