STATUS: Closed
TITLE: <Route ID>: approach locking release timer exceeds platform maximum
STATEMENT: >>>
Defect found during approach locking release test (ATR-xxx). The approach
locking release timer value for <Route ID> was set to <n+x> s, exceeding the
platform maximum of <n> s defined in APP-C-004.
Impact: parameter out of valid range; the data validator (APP-080) should have
rejected this value at compile time but did not due to an incorrect upper-bound
value in the validator configuration.
Fix applied:
  1. Application data parameter corrected to <n> s in <parameters.dsl>.
  2. Data validator configuration updated to enforce the correct upper limit.
  3. All parameter values re-checked against APP-C-004 ranges.
Re-test: ATR-xxx re-executed after fix; PASS. Regression tests for all
parameter range checks executed; all PASS. New baseline <APP-BL-yyy> generated.
